@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM SAP Analytics Cloud Service - Component Architecture

actor "BI User / Creator" as Creator
actor "Planner" as Planner
actor "Data Admin" as Admin
actor "Mobile User" as Mobile
actor "Third-Party App" as ThirdParty

node "Analytics Cloud Service Runtime" {
  component "AnalyticsServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api

  package "Domain Services" {
    component "Story & Dashboard\nManagement" as UX
    component "Planning &\nScenario Engine" as Planning
    component "Data Connectivity\n& Modeling" as DataConn
    component "Smart Capabilities\n(Predictions/ML)" as Smart
    component "Administration\n& User Management" as AdminSvc
    component "Mobile & Embedding" as MobileEmbed
  }

  database "AnalyticsStore\n(In-Memory Multi-Tenant)" as Store
}

cloud "SAP Datasphere" as Datasphere

Creator --> Api : Stories, Dashboards
Planner --> Api : Plans, What-If
Admin --> Api : Users, Connections, Overview
Mobile --> Api : Mobile Catalog
ThirdParty --> Api : Embed API

Api --> UX : route
Api --> Planning : route
Api --> DataConn : route
Api --> Smart : route
Api --> AdminSvc : route
Api --> MobileEmbed : route

UX --> Store : persist stories/dashboards
Planning --> Store : persist plans
DataConn --> Store : persist connections/datasets/models
Smart --> Store : persist predictions
AdminSvc --> Store : persist users

DataConn ..> Datasphere : optional integration

note right of Smart
Smart Capabilities:
- What-if scenario simulation
- Automated ML (time series,
  classification, regression)
- Prediction with confidence metrics
end note

@enduml
